{"tid":2141431,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大傳銷佬整合","createTime":"2020-08-05T16:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T15:39:54.000Z","uid":104052,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"19c767870e57603d43c150fd0bf4c25b5b9afd47","tid":2141431,"uid":104052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:08:52.000Z","msg":"###傳銷佬整合###<br />\n<blockquote>中大確診傳銷佬Wallace<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvy91ut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcvy91ut.jpg&h=40c88379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvy91ut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcvy91ut.jpg&h=40c88379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9iCbvnN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9iCbvnN.png&h=b861e24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mzYazF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mzYazF.png&h=b3fe2509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>仲有同播毒傳銷佬拍住上嘅roommate Leo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEbLDRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEbLDRh.jpg&h=7b36cf49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Xj1S0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Xj1S0H.jpg&h=000a2004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YBSZFH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YBSZFH.jpg&h=1ae315ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWsSfem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWsSfem.png&h=e01379fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bCQAc03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCQAc03.png&h=ea6cf154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>仲有呢個傳二代, 同中大確診傳銷佬同一條team 嘅Nathan 鄭尚賢, 老豆老母係佢出世之前就做傳銷, 係外國讀完書返黎就做傳銷, 仲要成日走入黎湯宿屈傳銷佬蛇, 成日同確診傳銷佬訓埋同一間房, 但而家仲係出面逍遙快活緊, 咁高危係時候推到佢地一齊喺隔離中心團聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有非中大人黎屈蛇又唔知算唔算係非法闖入之類嗰啲呢, 求一d 有法律知識嘅ching 幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TZpUbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TZpUbp.jpg&h=9ecd38ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fq6zwYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffq6zwYj.png&h=57889174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x24M7wG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx24M7wG.png&h=a176eceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBRDecK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBRDecK.png&h=ba3d1a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>仲有呢個Peter , 就係中大確診傳銷佬Wallace 同 Roommate Leo 對上細Team個大佬, under IT Carrie 柒婆 同Sunny 嘅, 繼續推到佢地仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXV8BFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXV8BFE.jpg&h=c854c99b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cp95DT6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCp95DT6.png&h=84ff14f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>白衫猥瑣男就係Sunny，已經係再上去嘅大team leader 嚟，聽講成日食下面手下d傳銷雞，成幾百個傳銷佬進貢畀佢，其他嗰啲都係佢d頭馬，如果唔係點會做傳銷做到上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收到風佢哋夾埋買咗五六層, Sunny 自己好似買咗四層, 可想而知佢地食左幾多下線錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sm1Pttz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSm1Pttz.jpg&h=df447d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2XZQXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2XZQXa.jpg&h=ce296bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>呢個就叫IT Carrie,佢哋嗰team最大粒嘅就係佢, 好似係佢地入面d 位叫做43, 佢d 𡃁叫佢做Carrie 姐, 果然叫得Carrie 嘅都係柒婆黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  IT carrie 電話62237342<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEQXqvL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEQXqvL.png&h=022340cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3utxaM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3utxaM.jpg&h=3cd9b731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWhZDQO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWhZDQO.png&h=b4ba65a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fkr35vQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkr35vQ.png&h=95745771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7c400543f68eaf39b9ab2d17ce42965b499fdd62","tid":2141431,"uid":104052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>######傳銷公司如何呃人懶人包######<br />\n可能大家都唔知到底亮碧思係點樣呃人，下面俾少少大概嘅idea 大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋就算俾人呃咗都好，佢哋係有得退款架，就算俾人呃咗都好，唔好好似中大傳銷佬咁搵其他人做水魚咁傻豬豬喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>希望中大傳銷佬Wallace 同佢Roommate Leo肺炎好番之後可以回頭是岸，拿拿聲返去 『公司』退錢然後比心機打工還返財仔筆數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你先比$5000入會費 再比$62569買一個位 再開一條line 一條line有6個位 <strong><span class=\"red\">$62569x6=$375414 </span></strong>好似樹圖咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你要比曬大數先 點比呢？<br />\n佢哋會打通晒所有財仔 幫你一條龍服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括你1.戶口儲蓄 2.信用卡限額 3.你有正常收入 大概一萬蚊都可以 佢就可以祝你去<span class=\"red\"><strong>搵財仔借人工23定唔知22倍</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多除小補一定夠數 <br />\n然你會揾6個朋友借名頂住6個位先<br />\n然後就開始揾水魚 同岀黎見多啲朋友 比佢地知你好揾得 自然會有人問你做緊咩公司？ 多數比人問得依句 就會叫你岀黎傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉你個水魚朋友去打霧=洗腦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由<span class=\"red\"><strong>中午12點到凌晨三點不停洗你腦</strong></span><br />\n不停有人分享自己有幾搵得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗到你位水魚朋友暈陀陀 就叫佢比$5000入會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再洗多幾獲 就<span class=\"red\"><strong>叫你位水魚朋友比$62569 買你一個位</strong></span> 叫番個借名朋友同水魚朋友換名改番資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">如此類推 揾齊六色戰隊水魚軍團 頂你下面六個位之後 你就會收番$62569x6=$375414 填完數之後<br />\n每拉一個人你都會有新人佣金收</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你既下線水魚軍團又會開始將水魚大軍發揚光大 每個人各自開一條line 一共六條line <strong><span class=\"red\">一共36個位$62569x6=$375414 x6 =$2252484 </span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">佢哋每揾一個人 你都會收到新人佣金</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[size=5][b][red]但你既下線付出既錢唔可以多過你 所以你只可以好似打機買VIP一樣 不斷課金，所有錢最後都係俾晒亮碧思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n######肺炎傳銷群組地址######<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何文田亞皆老街怡安閣一二四號一樓及地庫一層<br />\nFrancine Holdings Limited（簡稱 FC明昇）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />旺角西洋菜南街二號Ａ銀城廣場五樓及六樓<br />\nFrancine Holdings Limited（簡稱 FC明昇）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沙田石門安耀街二號新都廣場九及十二樓<br />\nFrancine Holdings Limited（簡稱 FC明昇）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尖沙咀漆咸道南十九號帝后廣場二樓及三樓 Estebel Spa<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長沙灣永康街五十五號金百盛中心地下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />灣仔禮頓道一至七號愉景樓一樓及二樓<br />\nDigital Crown Holdings (HK) Ltd（簡稱DC盛朗）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長沙灣長沙灣道八二八號萬利中心一、三及七樓<br />\nBelle Venture Holding (HK) Ltd（簡稱BV百麗）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尖沙咀東科學館道十四號新文華中心Ｂ座一樓及二樓<br />\nSibellac Holdings Ltd （簡稱詩貝朗SH）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />銅鑼灣軒尼詩道五五五號東角中心（舊翼）十三及十四樓<br />\n亮碧思集團（香港）有限公司<br />\n####SG/LB/FC/BV/Dc/明昇/Star global /亮碧思####<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#####亮碧思Francine/ SG/Star globle 傳銷狗呃人嘅銀碼#####<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />20位置$5000+$210<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />38位置$62569<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />41位置$437,983 (會叫你跑財仔）<br />\n<br />\n########退單方法#######<br />\n20位置，可以隨時退錢，$5000不是比公司收袋的，是你的貴人袋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係你朋友銀包入面，準備拎去還錢比財仔！記得企硬要退！就可以原銀奉還！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n38位置，$62569 ，14日內退9折，90日內退7折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n41位置，同上！但記得要簽文件！為求自保，請保留所有你同upline的對話內容！必要時可以報警！佢地最鐘意唔開單，私呑下線單錢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n##########忠告##########<br />\n唔該各位被昆嘅唔好做道德撚，水得你嘅你仲當朋友！我真心覺得係on9,當然你要同垃圾老千做朋友你嘅事，但我哋唔希望再見到又要問點退但又要話怕冇fd做呀，想救返佢出嚟個啲廢話！麻煩照照鏡救撚咗自己先攞返錢先！做定唔做，諗清楚先好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉自：<a href=\"https://t.me/becareful_LB_Laminated_marketing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbecareful_LB_Laminated_marketing&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdB